      "span_text": "Recombinant plasmid pBAD18-Cm-eptC was obtained by pGEMT-eptC double digestion with SalI and PvuII and subcloning into pBAD18-Cm doubly digested with SalI and SmaI. This construct was transformed into K. pneumoniae core LPS mutants and eptC was expressed from the arabinose-inducible and glucose-repressible pBAD18-Cm promoter  ."
